      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/12/35428890/94aa30ae75b8c7c6a9c64ab05bd5dda7_7212127566840369071.png",
                "id": "talent67684",
                "key": "Boxcutter",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Boxcutter"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Urgent Neko Parcel</span> and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shield of Safe Transport</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Urgent Neko Parcel</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When Kirara is your active character, after you switch characters:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span> and draw 1 card.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">U</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">sage(s): 1 </span>(Can stack. Max 2 stacks.)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Shield of Safe Transport</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Shield</span><br>Grants <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2 Shield points</span> to your active character.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/12/35428890/e1d9ab13ba19969303b42dbee09f59e7_330907643430500216.png",
                "id": "talent32127",
                "key": "Meow-teor Kick",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Meow-teor Kick"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cat Grass Cardamom</span> on the opponent's side of the field.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Cat Grass Cardamom</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After the side of the field that this card is on has played 2 Action Cards:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span> to the active character on that side.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/12/35428890/ec58f74c94bbd19ecbb0c33f972f5788_3655570316350431857.png",
                "id": "talent12558",
                "key": "Secret Art: Surprise Dispatch",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Secret Art: Surprise Dispatch"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Dendro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that greants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/12/35428890/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_1202095432895630394.png",
                "id": "talent68553",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Shield</span></strong><br>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/12/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_2431042562936159974.png",
                "id": "talent65210",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
